---
title: Seared Duck in Apricot Sauce with Rosemary Roasted Potatoes
description: Duck dinner at home? Oh yes, luxury is coming to your kitchen tonight! Juicy duck breasts are seared until the skin is crispy and golden-brown, then drizzled with mouthwatering apricot sauce. The potatoes complement the tart sauce and a crisp salad finishes it off!
